      "content": "Wait, you're saying the impact will be \"minimal\"? I don't know. My margins are pretty tight, and if my labor costs spike, I might have to raise prices or even cut staff. Doesn't that potentially hurt the very same workers the wage hike is supposed to help? I'd like to hear the other side of the economic argument here.",
